  "prompt": "How many ways are there to pronounce Quora?",
  "response": "The name \"Quora\" is typically pronounced in one standard way: /\u02c8kw\u0254\u02d0r\u0259/ or KWOHR-\u0259. This pronunciation is derived from the combination of the first syllable \"Quo\" sounding like \"Kwo\" and the second syllable \"ra\" sounding like \"ruh.\"\n\nWhile it's possible for individuals to pronounce it differently due to accents or misinterpretations, the generally accepted and intended pronunciation is as described above. Therefore, there is effectively one correct way to pronounce \"Quora.\"",
